We have this little black box function called query data. You don't need to worry about that.

00:03:18.000 --> 00:03:22.000
But basically you can pull location and then various pollutants

00:03:22.000 --> 00:03:26.000
that go with that location. And in your Cordo doc, you have a plot,

00:03:26.000 --> 00:03:30.000
you have some statistics that you pull out of that data, and you have a table.

